It's nice to see a few more
A's this time around...

8
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,934
including Mr. Bowden's,
of course.

9
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:15,674
This concludes our week
on the Holocaust.

10
00:01:22,482 --> 00:01:25,781
It you wanna know more, you may
find the Santo Donato library...

11
